176
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:26,680
[Ge Chuan, apothecary]

177
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:27,890
Not a chance

178
00:11:30,270 --> 00:11:32,010
[Xu Jia, personal guard of Duke Su]

179
00:11:30,530 --> 00:11:31,940
Your Highness

180
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:45,430
[Yuedan Commentary
at Ju Shui Pavilion]

