219
00:14:44,650 --> 00:14:45,980
What do you wish to know?

220
00:14:46,170 --> 00:14:47,870
When will I die?

221
00:14:48,930 --> 00:14:50,140
Why?

222
00:14:50,230 --> 00:14:53,630
