238
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:34,250
Let me perform a ritual there
and everything will be okay

239
00:16:34,250 --> 00:16:35,790
What if...

240
00:16:36,070 --> 00:16:37,460
I turn you down?

241
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:44,550
Well then, I can only

