261
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,510
That's my new fragrant powder

262
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:25,270
Excuse me

263
00:19:26,210 --> 00:19:27,280
Mister,

264
00:19:27,360 --> 00:19:29,500
