by saving your life

269
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:41,600
It's you

270
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,000
Till we meet again

271
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,030
No, no

272
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:46,470
Since you've come this far,

273
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:48,410
