274
00:19:48,490 --> 00:19:50,920
can you take me to the stream?

275
00:19:52,180 --> 00:19:53,740
Then, tell me

276
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:56,200
What's your intention...

277
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:58,450
